Class RawResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reinert.requestor.core.RawResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeserializableResponse, DeserializableResponseInProcess, HasHeaders, IncomingResponse, InProcess, MutableResponse, MutableSerializedResponse, Processable, ProcessableResponse, Response, ResponseInProcess, Saver, SerializedResponse, SerializedResponseInProcess, Store

    public class RawResponse
extends Object
implements MutableResponse, DeserializableResponse, ProcessableResponse
    Represents a response just received by the request and prepared to be processed.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
